<h5 id="kubernetes_cluster"><a href="#kubernetes_cluster">Kubernetes Cluster</a></h5>
<p>Polaris is designed to run on Kubernetes platform. It requires a cluster with atleast 1 manager and 3 nodes satisfying following configurations.</p>

<b>Memory :</b> 20 GB <br>
<b>CPU :</b> 18 CPUs <br>
<b>Disk Space :</b> 400 GB <br>

<br><br>

<h5 id="postgresql"><a href="#postgresql">PostgreSQL Instance</a></h5>
<p>Polaris requires a PostgreSQL instance with few databases created. Recommended configuration for PostgreSQL is,</p>

<b>Memory :</b> 8 GB <br>
<b>CPU :</b> 4 CPUs <br>
<b>Disk Space :</b> 200 GB <br>

<br><br>

